### <a name="input_deployment_subnet_name"></a> [deployment\_subnet\_name](#input\_deployment\_subnet\_name)

Description: Optional. The name of the subnet to create for the deployment scripts. If set, overrides the default name 'snet-deployment'.

Type: `string`

Default: `"snet-deployment"`

### <a name="input_enable_telemetry"></a> [enable\_telemetry](#input\_enable\_telemetry)

Description: Optional. Enable/Disable module telemetry for AVM submodules.

Type: `bool`

Default: `true`

### <a name="input_hub_virtual_network_resource_id"></a> [hub\_virtual\_network\_resource\_id](#input\_hub\_virtual\_network\_resource\_id)

Description: Optional. The resource ID of the existing hub virtual network. If provided, a peering from spoke to hub will be created.

Type: `string`

Default: `""`

### <a name="input_network_appliance_ip_address"></a> [network\_appliance\_ip\_address](#input\_network\_appliance\_ip\_address)

Description: Optional. The IP address of the network appliance (e.g. firewall) that will be used to route traffic to the internet. Required to create the egress lockdown UDR.

Type: `string`

Default: `""`

### <a name="input_route_spoke_traffic_internally"></a> [route\_spoke\_traffic\_internally](#input\_route\_spoke\_traffic\_internally)

Description: Optional. Define whether to route spoke-internal traffic within the spoke network. If false, traffic will be sent to the hub network. Default is false.

Type: `bool`

Default: `false`

### <a name="input_spoke_application_gateway_subnet_address_prefix"></a> [spoke\_application\_gateway\_subnet\_address\_prefix](#input\_spoke\_application\_gateway\_subnet\_address\_prefix)

Description: Optional. CIDR of the spoke Application Gateway subnet. If empty, no Application Gateway subnet or NSG will be created.

Type: `string`

Default: `""`

### <a name="input_spoke_application_gateway_subnet_name"></a> [spoke\_application\_gateway\_subnet\_name](#input\_spoke\_application\_gateway\_subnet\_name)

Description: Optional. The name of the subnet to create for the spoke application gateway. If set, overrides the default name 'snet-agw'. Only used when the subnet CIDR is provided.

Type: `string`

Default: `"snet-agw"`

### <a name="input_spoke_infra_subnet_name"></a> [spoke\_infra\_subnet\_name](#input\_spoke\_infra\_subnet\_name)

Description: Optional. The name of the subnet to create for the spoke infrastructure. If set, overrides the default name 'snet-infra'.

Type: `string`

Default: `"snet-infra"`

### <a name="input_spoke_private_endpoints_subnet_name"></a> [spoke\_private\_endpoints\_subnet\_name](#input\_spoke\_private\_endpoints\_subnet\_name)

Description: Optional. The name of the subnet to create for the spoke private endpoints. If set, overrides the default name 'snet-pep'.

Type: `string`

Default: `"snet-pep"`

Description: Optional. The storage account type to use for the jump box.

Type: `string`

Default: `"Standard_LRS"`

### <a name="input_tags"></a> [tags](#input\_tags)

Description: Optional. Tags to apply to spoke resources.

Type: `map(string)`

Default: `{}`

### <a name="input_vm_admin_password"></a> [vm\_admin\_password](#input\_vm\_admin\_password)

Default: `""`

### <a name="input_vm_size"></a> [vm\_size](#input\_vm\_size)

Description: Optional. The size of the virtual machine to create when vm\_jumpbox\_os\_type != 'none'.

Type: `string`

Default: `""`

Description: Optional. The name of the subnet to create for the jump box.

### <a name="input_vm_zone"></a> [vm\_zone](#input\_vm\_zone)
